parameters.name: ClusterId
parameters.description: The ID of the cluster that you want to scan.

parameters.name: Dealed
parameters.description:
The handling status. Valid values:

*   **Y**: handled.
*   **N**: unhandled.
*   **A**: all.

parameters.name: ImageDigest
parameters.description: The SHA-256 value of the image digest.

parameters.name: RepoId
parameters.description: The ID of the Container Registry repository.

parameters.name: RepoInstanceId
parameters.description:
The ID of the Container Registry instance.

>  You can call the [DescribeImageInstances](~~DescribeImageInstances~~) operation to obtain the ID.

parameters.name: RepoRegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the Container Registry repository.

parameters.name: ScanRange
parameters.description: The assets that you want to scan.

parameters.name: Uuids
parameters.description: The IDs of the instances that you want to scan.
